        <abstract>
            <p>He has gone through the whole embryology of the Crustacea and has arrived at a pretty well-established genealogy of the whole class; has even tried to write a history of the whole tribe. Finds he cannot adopt the old separation of Orders in the Class; the limits between them are indistinct.</p> 
<p>Would like to study embryology of <hi rend="italic">Limulus</hi>. Asks CD’s help in obtaining a female specimen.</p> 
            <p>Outlines his proposal to establish a marine zoological station.</p>
        </abstract>
